        "comment": "Thursday will be fairly clear, with some low cloud in the mid mountains at first. Some variable cumulus cloud will develop during the day. There will be only a light westerly to north-westerly wind. It will be warmer. Temperatures at 1500 m will be around 6 \u00b0C mid-day and at 2500 m around 4 \u00b0C."
